</div>
<p style="line-height: 2;">then we can conclude that <span class="lurch-atom" contenteditable="false" data-metadata_type="&quot;expression&quot;" data-metadata_lurch-notation="&quot;pie&quot;"><span class="lurch-atom-body"><span class="ML__latex"><span class="ML__base"><span class="ML__text">ðŸ¥§</span></span></span></span></span> is a theorem.</p>
